# Business Viewpoint – SoilSense

## 1. Overview

According to ISO/IEC 30141:2024, the Business Viewpoint focuses on understanding how the capabilities of an IoT system create value for stakeholders, support business objectives, and influence system owners and managers.

For the SoilSense system, the Business Viewpoint analyzes how environmental monitoring, remote control, historical data management, and interoperability contribute to operational efficiency and informed decision-making.

