## 4. System Description from a Business Perspective

SoilSense is an IoT-based environmental monitoring and control platform composed of multiple ESP32-C6 nodes connected through an OpenThread mesh network.

The system collects:

* Humidity measurements
* Temperature measurements
* Water level measurements

The platform also includes:

* Remote pump control
* Real-time monitoring
* Historical data storage
* Alert generation
* Dashboard visualization
* Secure communication between devices

Data is transmitted through MQTT and CoAP protocols and integrated through Matter services to provide a unified monitoring and control experience.

