## 7. Service Blueprint

### Service Flow

```text
User
  │
  ▼
Dashboard
  │
  ▼
Matter Controller
  │
  ▼
Border Router
  │
  ▼
Gateway
  │
  ▼
ESP32-C6 Sensor Nodes
  │
  ▼
Sensors and Actuator
```

### Service Description

1. Sensors acquire environmental data.
2. Sensor nodes publish information through the network.
3. The Gateway aggregates and forwards data.
4. The Border Router manages OpenThread connectivity.
5. Matter services manage device integration and control.
6. The Dashboard presents information to users.
7. Users can send commands to actuators through the same infrastructure.

