## 8. Business Benefits

### Operational Efficiency

Continuous monitoring reduces the need for manual inspections and routine supervision.

### Improved Decision-Making

Real-time data and historical records support evidence-based decisions.

### Remote Operation

Users can access information and control actuators without being physically present.

### Scalability

Additional sensor nodes can be incorporated without redesigning the overall architecture.

### Interoperability

The use of MQTT, CoAP, IPv6, OpenThread, and Matter facilitates integration with future systems.

### Service Availability

OpenThread mesh networking provides self-healing capabilities that improve service continuity.

### Long-Term Sustainability

Open standards reduce vendor dependency and support future system evolution.

